  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Discord</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/075046a5e2659e46f714e035ffbb7c10.avif?t=1748829472\" width=616 height=127 /></span>5Wxh4WmTbY</h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 'Getting Over It' style game. Play as a cute dog. Lick, grip, and swing with your tongue. Overcome 8 distinct levels: Big Swings, Ice Sliding, Space Drifting, Volcano Escaping, etc. No checkpoints. Has collectables, leaderboards, and dog customisation.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obviously, we learned from ‘Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy’, but the game wasn't all about hurting a certain kind of person. We were trying to find a balance between psychological horror and classic level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We learned Nintendo-style level design patterns. Each level has a unique element running through it and combined with other elements to create challenges. The entire game has 8 normal levels, 4 types of mechanisms, and 3 types of level mechanisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is undoubtedly challenging, and you may experience repeated failures. However, with practice and experimentation, you will gradually master the art of tongue skills and gain control over your dog's movements, allowing you to navigate forward with flexibility and precision.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 'Getting Over It' style game. Play as a cute dog. Lick, grip, and swing with your tongue. Overcome 8 distinct levels: Big Swings, Ice Sliding, Space Drifting, Volcano Escaping, etc. No checkpoints. Has collectables, leaderboards, and dog customisation.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/e35c105cee9f77a3f1fdd575d224cf63.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obviously, we learned from ‘Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy’, but the game wasn't all about hurting a certain kind of person. We were trying to find a balance between psychological horror and classic level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/2ef12368ce4a46548469244b8ebdc65a.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We learned Nintendo-style level design patterns. Each level has a unique element running through it and combined with other elements to create challenges. The entire game has 8 normal levels, 4 types of mechanisms, and 3 types of level mechanisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.poster.avif?t=1748829472\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.webm?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1990540/extras/799e53db291a39690dc2b0325f22ac89.mp4?t=1748829472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is undoubtedly challenging, and you may experience repeated failures. However, with practice and experimentation, you will gradually master the art of tongue skills and gain control over your dog's movements, allowing you to navigate forward with flexibility and precision.</p>",
